      "description": "FEA-predicted construct stiffness compared against bench measurements from two independent laboratories. Mean absolute percentage error 4.2%; E/uval = 1.31, within the acceptance bound of 1.96. Uncertainty in experimental measurements propagated using standard ASTM repeatability estimates. UQ was performed via Monte Carlo sampling over material property distributions; we plan to extend with sensitivity analysis to rank the relative contribution of each input parameter in future work.",
